rComments: Very easy marker, very clear! No exam, midterm was a breeze. Works read were also very interesting and expanded my skills in interpretive reading. Very nice man, and I hope to take another class with him!

He is an amazing prof! He was interactive with us and he didn`t just stand up there and drone on. There was a lot of activities to do in class that really enhanced learning. He was readily available for communication either after class or via e-mail. Best prof  ever!
Very helpful. He really wants you to learn something.
As long students follow the guidelines there shouldn't be too much of a problem.  Yes, he is strict, but...that may be expected.
He's a tough one, but fair. My writing has improved a lot since I took his class. Recommend him - but you need to be willing to work hard.
Prof split class into two parts, half lecture and half workshop which made the time go by much faster - and kept things interesting. Fair marker. Willing to help and answer all questions.
Easy to understand, fair marker. Lets the class out early sometimes.
